    <!-- About Section -->
    <div class="neba-panel">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--neba-blue-700)] mb-4">About NEBA</h2>
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
            <p class="text-[var(--neba-text)] mb-3">
                The New England Bowling Association (NEBA) has been the premier bowling tour in the region since 1963.
                We bring together the best bowlers from across New England to compete in challenging tournaments
                at top-quality bowling centers throughout the year.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[var(--neba-text)] mb-3">
                Our tour features multiple divisions and award categories, including Bowler of the Year,
                Rookie of the Year, Senior Bowler of the Year, and more. We celebrate excellence through
                our Hall of Fame and maintain comprehensive historical records of champions and achievements.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[var(--neba-text)]">
                Whether you're a seasoned competitor or new to tournament bowling, NEBA offers opportunities
                to test your skills, build lasting friendships, and be part of a rich bowling tradition.
            </p>
        </div>
